Larry Medeles Ismael Orjuela Natalie Peyton Mickie Snear Clay Venezia Charles Subject FW Things youll never hear women say Things youll never hear women say You know Ive been complaining a lot lately I dont blame you for ignoring me The new woman in my office is a real beauty and a stripper too I invited her over for dinner on Friday While you were in the bathroom they went for it on fourth down and missed If they can hold them to a field goal theyll still cover Bar food again Great I liked that wedding even more than ours You know your exgirlfriend has class That woman is wearing the same outfit as I am Cool Im gonna go talk to her Lets just leave the toilet seat up at all times then you dont have to mess with it anymore Honey isnt tonight your night out with the boys You need your time with them Its only the third quarter we should order a couple more pitchers My mother is going to take care of the tab so order another round for you and your friends Im so happy with my new hairstyle I dont think Ill ever change it again Damn I love when my pillow smells like your cigars and beer You passed out before brushing your teeth again ya big silly You are so much smarter than my father Are you sure youve had enough to drink Ive decided to stop wearing clothes around the house Youre so sexy when youre hung over I love it when you change channels all the time It really helps me find out what else is on Lets subscribe to Hustler If you need me Ill be out painting the house I love it when you ride your Harley I just wish you had more time to ride Honey our new neighbors
